Lewis Hamilton won the Chinese Grand Prix with Mercedes team-mate Nico Rosberg .
Rosberg was furious with Hamilton in the press conference after the race .
Hamilton claimed Rosberg had severely compromised his strategy and left him under unnecessary pressure from Ferrari's Sebastian Vettel .
But Rosberg claimed Hamilton was 'driving very slowly' in the first pit-stops .
The Brit said: 'I had no real threat from Nico throughout the whole race'